  Home  SEC Filings  SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) Files An 8-K Other Events     SEC Filings  SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) Files An 8-K Other Events  ByME Staff 8-k -April 18, 2017 11  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) Files An 8-K Other Events

Item 8.01 Other Events.


Due to the audit procedures still being performed on certain
transactions closed in January, 2017, our annual report on Form
10-K for the year ended December 31, 2016 is unable to be filed
on April 17, 2017, the date of which was indicated in our NT
10-K/A filed on March 16, 2017. Upon the completion of the audit
procedures, we will file the annual report on Form 10-K for the
year ended on December 31, 2016 as promptly as possible.

           

 About SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) San Lotus Holding Inc. is a development-stage company. The Company is focused primarily on the development and marketing of its business model and Website. It plans to market global travel products to the retiring baby boomer generation in the Asian markets. Its travel services entity in Taiwan will provide both outbound travel services for customers based in Taiwan and inbound travel services for customers based abroad and coming to Taiwan. It will market its products and services to the travel population in Taiwan and abroad through its Website, www.sanlotusholding.com. The Company intends to use the cars, with hired drivers, to provide car service for its customers from the airport to their hotels or other desired destinations upon their arrival in California. Its products and services offered include transportation, such as airlines, buses, car rentals, railways and cruises; accommodation, including hotels, resorts and cruises, and packaged holidays and local tours. SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) Recent Trading Information SAN LOTUS HOLDING INC. (OTCMKTS:SLOT) closed its last trading session 00.000 at 0.925 with shares trading hands.
