					Full Description



San Lotus Holding Inc., incorporated on June 21, 2011, is a development-stage company. The Company is focused primarily on the development and marketing of its business model and Website. The Company is in the initial stages of opening a travel agency in Taiwan, Republic of China. It plans to market global travel products to the retiring baby boomer generation in the Asian markets. Its travel services entity in Taiwan will provide both outbound travel services for customers based in Taiwan and inbound travel services for customers based abroad and coming to Taiwan. It will market its products and services to the travel population in Taiwan and abroad through its Website, www.sanlotusholding.com, as well as through services, such as Twitter and other media outlets.The Company intends to use the cars, with hired drivers, to provide car service for its customers from the airport to their hotels or other desired destinations upon their arrival in California. Its products and services offered include transportation, such as airlines, buses, car rentals, railways, cruises; accommodation, including hotels, resorts, cruises, and packaged holidays and local tours. It will operate in two sectors in the area of destination real estate development and travel agencies. The Company plans to cater to high-income individuals and affinity groups, such as private schools, alumni groups and wealth management organizations at banks and investment firms.The Company competes with Lion Travel, Cola Tour, EZ Travel, Star Travel, SET Tour, Royal Jet Way, Perfect Travel, Life Tour, China Airlines, EVA Airlines, American Express, Elements Innovation Co. Ltd., E United Group and Taiwan Land Development Inc.

» Full Overview of SLOT.PK







