San Lotus Holding Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 1:46 PM ET
Hotels, Restaurants and Leisure

Company Overview of San Lotus Holding Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
San Lotus Holding Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the provision of travel services, including hotel reservation, airline ticketing, and travel package services in the United States. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Hacienda Heights, California.


2387 South Hacienda BoulevardHacienda Heights, CA 91745United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 626-961-6522

www.sanlotusholding.com







Key Executives for San Lotus Holding Inc.


San Lotus Holding Inc. does not have any Key Executives recorded. 



San Lotus Holding Inc. Key Developments

San Lotus Holding Inc. Announces Board Appointments
May 22 17
On May 22, 2017, San Lotus Holding Inc. appointed Mr. Lai,Wen-Ching and Kwong. Edwin as Vice-Chairman. Kwong, Edwin is the President, CEO of GUI Corporations dba Mega Productions; HempCon Inc; and American Youth Obesity Research and Prevention Foundation. Lai Wen-Ching is Director of Hung Chin Machinery Co. Ltd. where he has served in such capacity since 1980. He is also General Manager of Shun Bin Industrial Co. Ltd. where he has held such position since 1985. Mr. Lai is also Director and Partner of Investment Yan Zi International Inc. and an independent consultant advising on various business matters for the Taichung City Government since 2005. The board of directors of the company approved to form following committees: The audit committee members are Lai, Wen-Ching, Lin, Mu-Chen and Yeh, Shun-Shan. The nomination committee member are Lai, Wen-Ching, Chen, Kuan-Yu and Yeh, Shun-Shan. The compensation committee member are Lai, Wen-Ching, Kwong, Edwin and                   Yeh, Shun-Shan.


San Lotus Holding Inc. Approves Amendments to its Bylaws
May 22 17
On May 22, 2017, the Board of Directors of San Lotus Holding Inc. approved to add and/or amend the Section 8 of Article II; the Section 2 and 13 of Article III; and Article VII in its bylaws.


San Lotus Holding Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 15 17
On 05/15/2017, San Lotus Holding Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


