San Lotus Holding Inc.


            
            San Lotus Holding, Inc. operates as a development stage company, which intends to provide travel and leisure services. It intends to provide both outbound travel services for customers based in Taiwan as well as inbound travel services for customers based abroad and coming to Taiwan. The company was founded on June 21, 2011 and is headquartered in Rosemead, CA.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


